# Privacy Notice
This privacy notice discloses the privacy practices for "Legroom for Google Flights" Chrome extension.
This privacy notice applies solely to information collected by this extension, and not for information
collected by your browser or by Google Flights.

## Data Collection
This extension does not collect any information about you, about your searches and about your usage.
This extension does not transmit any data online. 

## Security 
We take precautions to ensure that this extension is secure by keeping our accounts hygienic.
We keep you safe by not collecting any data through the extension.

## Registration
Registration is not required to use this extension.

## Cookies
Cookie is not required to use this extension.

## Third-party Website
This extension modifies content of Google Flights website at https://www.google.com/flights.
We do not collect information that you provide to Google Flights website.

## Analytics
We have access to aggregated usage information through Chrome Web Store as outlined by
Chrome Web Store privacy policy: https://developer.chrome.com/webstore/terms#privacy.

The information we get is limited to:
* The number of users who installed the extension.
* The number of users who use the extension.

We use this information to feel good for having made this extension.

## Personal Data for Support
When you contact us, through Chrome Web Store support or review page, or through Github, we will use
information that you have provided to respond to you, regarding the reason you contacted us.  
We will not share your information with any other third party other than the medium through which 
you contacted us (Chrome Web Store or Github).

## Closing
If you feel that we are not abiding by this privacy policy, you should contact us immediately by
filling a Github issue at https://github.com/dbugger/legroom/issues, contacting the developer through
Github or through Chrome Web Store extension support page at
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/legrooms-for-google-fligh/nhonfddkgankhjilponlbdccpabaaknp/support.

